            "type": "prose",
            "fields": {
                "body": "Vigil Care Staffing supplies vetted care-sector workers \u2014 healthcare assistants, support workers and healthcare cleaners \u2014 to care providers across Greater London. We help care homes, nursing homes, supported-living and specialist services fill rota gaps reliably, whether at short notice or as ongoing support.\n\nWe are a staffing agency, not a regulated care provider. Vigil Care Staffing does not operate regulated care services and is not CQC-registered. We supply the people; the care service remains yours to run, and we support your compliance through a careful, CQC-aligned recruitment and vetting process.",
